translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「人類は滅亡の危機！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Humanity is on the brink of extinction!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やばい！　マジやばい！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This is bad! Seriously bad!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そんな危機に立ち上がる奴はいないのか！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Isn't there anyone who will rise up in such a crisis?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ああ、いた！　その男とは一体！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Yes, there is! Who is this man exactly?!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「皆様、お馴染み！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Everyone, familiar to you all!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あの鬼畜戦士のランス様だー！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's that ruthless warrior, Lord Rance!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: きゃーっ、格好いいー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kyaa! So cool!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ってなわけで、第二次魔人戦争のお話ー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "So then, here is the story of the Second Demon War—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、後ろの画像だけど、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh, about the image in the back,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦争は逐次状況が変わるので、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: since the war situation changes bit by bit,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あくまでも開戦時の様子ね？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: this only shows the state at the start of the war, okay?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さて、魔人と人類が大規模に戦ったのは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Now, large scale battles between demons and humanity

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 過去に二回ほどありました」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: have happened about twice in the past.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「藤原石丸が率いるJAPAN、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "JAPAN led by Ishimaru Fujiwara,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: M・M・ルーンが率いる聖魔教団」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and the Holy Demon Cult led by M.M. Rune.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「しかし、魔軍の圧倒的な強さを前に、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, faced with the overwhelming strength of the demon army,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どちらもこてんぱんに負けてしまいました」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: both were thoroughly defeated.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「今度は……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This time...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス様率いる人類軍
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: the human army led by Lord Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ランス様なら……きっと……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If it's Lord Rance... surely...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「さあ、この戦争の結末がどうなるのか！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Now, what will be the outcome of this war!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私と一緒に見守りましょうね！　あなた！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's watch over it together! You!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ではでは、プレイの続きをどうぞ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well then, please continue playing!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「今回は異界のお話ー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This time, a story about a different world—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「この世界以外にも色々な世界があります。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There are many other worlds besides this one.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それを見つけたのがミラクル・トーさん
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The one who discovered them is Mr. Miracle To.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あなたの感覚で言えば原始時代な雰囲気で、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: From your perspective, there's a prehistoric atmosphere,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 恐竜が沢山いるサウルスモールとか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: like Saursmall, which is full of dinosaurs,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「巨人が一人でぽつーんといるだけの
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and Slowy Giant, a very lonely world with a single giant all alone.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とっても寂しい世界スロージャイアントなど
「この世には、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In this world,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そういう異世界が無数にあるってことね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: there are countless such different worlds.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「とは言っても、誰でも
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That said, not just anyone

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ほいほいと行き来できるわけじゃないの」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: can come and go freely.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「今、分かってるだけでも
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As far as we know now,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 異界に行き来できる人間はたった一人、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: there is only one human who can travel between other worlds,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔法レベル3であるミラクルさんだけね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and that is Miracle, who has magic level 3.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それ以外だと、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Other than that,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王も異界に行く魔法が使えるみたい」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: the Demon King also seems to have magic that can travel to other worlds.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「異界渡航能力はそれだけすごいってことね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This means the ability to travel to other worlds is that incredible.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……ここだけの話」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Just between us,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「別の異界に暮らす、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: there's someone living in another world,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一発お爺ちゃんも同じ能力持ちだわよね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Old Grandpa Ippatsu also has the same ability.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「本人曰く、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: According to him,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 儂はどこまでも行ける、どこまでも飛べる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I can go anywhere and fly anywhere.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とかなんとか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Or something like that.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ま、あっちとこっち、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, between there and here,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どこまで同じ世界観と思っていいか不明なので、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: it's unclear how much of the worldview is the same,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 深く考えないが吉、ていうかふわふわ案件」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so it's best not to think too deeply—it’s a fuzzy issue.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As far as we know now,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 異界に行き来できる人間はたった一人、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: there is only one human who can travel between other worlds,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔法レベル3であるミラクルさんだけね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and that is Miracle, who has magic level 3.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それ以外だと、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Other than that,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王も異界に行く魔法が使えるみたい」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: the Demon King also seems to have magic that can travel to other worlds.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「異界渡航能力はそれだけすごいってことね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This means the ability to travel to other worlds is that incredible.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「……ここだけの話」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Just between us,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「別の異界に暮らす、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: there's someone living in another world,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一発お爺ちゃんも同じ能力持ちだわよね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Old Grandpa Ippatsu also has the same ability.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「本人曰く、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: According to him,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 儂はどこまでも行ける、どこまでも飛べる。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I can go anywhere and fly anywhere.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とかなんとか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Or something like that.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ま、あっちとこっち、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, between there and here,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どこまで同じ世界観と思っていいか不明なので、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: it's unclear how much of the worldview is the same,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 深く考えないが吉、ていうかふわふわ案件」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so it's best not to think too deeply—it’s a fuzzy issue.
